FT  09 DEC 94 / UK Company News: Eve static at Pounds 2.5m midway
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Pre-tax profits at Eve Group, the USM-traded civil engineering company, were
little changed at Pounds 2.5m, against Pounds 2.51m, for the six months to
