FT  09 DEC 94 / Observer: First and last
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Whatever one thinks of the cogency of the arguments advanced by British Gas
to support chief executive Cedric Brown's remuneration levels, the logic at
work in the lower echelons of the utility is certainly less than perfect.
