company writes to an FT reader proudly announcing that, 'as a valued
customer, we thought you should be among the first to know about an
important new way to save money'. Sadly, the impact, if any, was rather
blunted by the accompanying sign-off: 'Act now and join the other three
million customers who already use this method . . .'
