<HEADLINE>
FT  09 DEC 94 / Budget Statement: How the chancellor balanced the books
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
   By ALISON SMITH
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
 -----------------------------------------------------------------------
SUMMARY OF PROPOSED MEASURES
 -----------------------------------------------------------------------
(positive number adds to PSBR) Pounds million
Measures already announced          1994-95  1995-96  1996-97  1997-98
