FT  08 DEC 94 / Observer: Commandeered
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
How exciting - an invitation for Observer to toast the festive season in the
company of The International Security Command of the Foreign and
Commonwealth Office. Some very hush-hush gathering of top military bods, no
doubt.
